OL,3,C'The Conservative Party is over,' says
OL,4,CMP Danny Kruger in defection to Reform
OL,5,CUK
OL,7,FFormer Conservative MP Danny Kruger
OL,8,Fhas joined Reform UK in a defection
OL,9,Fannounced on Monday.
OL,11,FSpeaking at a joint press conference
OL,12,Fwith Nigel Farage, Kruger claimed,
OL,13,F"the Conservative Party is over," but
OL,14,Fthat its "failure" had made way for
OL,15,FReform as an alternative.
OL,17,F"The flame is passing from one torch
OL,18,Fto another," said the MP for East
OL,19,FWiltshire, describing his decision to
OL,20,Fdefect as "personally painful."
