OL,12,FIntroducing Danny Kruger to the
OL,13,Fpodium, Nigel Farage told reporters
OL,14,FKruger would lead a department
OL,15,Fpreparing Reform UK for government.
OL,17,F"Our mission is not just to overthrow
OL,18,Fthe current system, it is to restore
OL,19,Fit," Kruger elaborated.
