OL,7,FAdding: "If you are serious about
OL,8,Fsaving our country... We want your
OL,9,Fhelp," before calling for people to
OL,10,Fjoin the party as well as provide
OL,11,F"confidential advice," if they worked
OL,12,Fin the "public sector or military."
OL,14,FAddressing what he viewed as the
OL,15,Ffailure of his former party, Kruger
OL,16,Fsaid: "We have had a year of stasis
OL,17,Fand drift and the sham unity that
OL,18,Fcomes from not doing anything bold or
OL,19,Fdifficult or controversial and the
OL,20,Fresult is in the polls.
