OL,3,C'The Conservative Party is over,' says
OL,4,CMP Danny Kruger in defection to Reform
OL,5,CUK
OL,7,F"And those voters aren't coming back,
OL,8,Fand every day, more and more people
OL,9,Fare joining them in deserting the
OL,10,Fparty that has failed."
OL,12,FHe added: "This is my tragic
OL,13,Fconclusion: the Conservative Party is
OL,14,Fover, over as a national party, over
OL,15,Fas the principal opposition to the
OL,16,Fleft."
OL,18,FDanny Kruger has been an MP since 2019
OL,19,Fand was serving as Shadow Work and
OL,20,FPensions Secretary prior to his
OL,21,Fdefection.
